{"id":232617974,"title":"記錄熱量請益","content":"因為前陣子受傷\n去看醫生的時候發現自己又變胖了\n因為目前還沒辦法運動\n所以想先從飲食下手\n想請問一下我這樣記錄的方式是對的嗎？\n\n尤其是晚餐的部分\n我是吃一個滷雞腿便當\n然後飯一半而已\n重量都亂估(上網查一格菜大概是25~30克)\n真的沒什麼概念\n因為我覺得自己也沒吃特別少\n可是總熱量離基礎代謝率還有滿大一段距離的\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/p1fz6Ae.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/3n0Chdp.jpg\n\n然後這是今天的營養素比例\n想問我設定的目標比例可以嗎？\n(有在檢討蛋白質吃太少了😂)\nhttps://i.imgur.com/62cORU5.jpg","excerpt":"因為前陣子受傷，去看醫生的時候發現自己又變胖了，因為目前還沒辦法運動，所以想先從飲食下手，想請問一下我這樣記錄的方式是對的嗎？尤其是晚餐的部分，我是吃一個滷雞腿便當，然後飯一半而已，重量都亂估（上網查","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"8a2a0b9a-7664-49b0-bff7-58389ef73a0d","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-03T09:56:37.424Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-03T10:06:53.897Z","commentCount":8,"likeCount":16,"tags":[],"topics":["記錄","熱量","減肥","飲食","疑問"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"減肥","forumAlias":"weight_loss","school":"中國醫藥大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":16}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/p1fz6Ae.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/3n0Chdp.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/62cORU5.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"dbd77396-9c5a-4fc6-a59d-e48f64503da2","url":"https://i.imgur.com/p1fz6Ael.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/p1fz6Ael.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/p1fz6Ael.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-03T09:56:37.424Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-03T10:06:53.897Z"},{"id":"dbd77396-9c5a-4fc6-a59d-e48f64503da2","url":"https://i.imgur.com/p1fz6Ae.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/p1fz6Ae","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/p1fz6Ael.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-03T09:56:37.424Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-03T10:06:53.897Z"},{"id":"672e735a-0dda-452f-a7ba-d